description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 44, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 132, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 3 for East, Leverage for South, and 2 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30443-73621-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [132 Votes, Top 15% Score]
